Interface BukkitImplAdapter<T>

All Superinterfaces:
IBukkitAdapter
All Known Subinterfaces:
IDelegateBukkitImplAdapter<T>
public interface BukkitImplAdapter<T> extends IBukkitAdapter
An interface for adapters of various Bukkit implementations.
